---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Digital Marketing for Small Business &#8212; Sydney SME"
  description="SNAV Marketing helps Sydney small businesses compete online with Google Ads, SEO, social media and lead generation. Affordable, results-focused digital marketing for SMEs."
  canonical="/industries/small-business"
>
  <section class="industry-hero">
    <div class="container-lg">
      <p class="eyebrow">Industry Specialists</p>
      <div class="hero-icon">🏢</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Punch Above Your Weight Online.<br />Win More Customers.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Your Sydney small business doesn't need a massive marketing budget &#8212; it needs a smart strategy. SNAV gives SMEs the same digital firepower as big brands, without the big price tag.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Grow My Business</a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="btn-secondary">See Pricing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-lg two-col">
      <div>
        <h2 class="h2">You're Up Against Big Brands With Big Budgets. Let's Level the Playing Field.</h2>
        <p class="body-text">Large chains can outspend you on TV and billboards. But digital marketing is the great equaliser &#8212; a smart SME strategy will consistently out-rank, out-engage and out-convert a lazy big brand.</p>
        <p class="body-text">SNAV works with all types of Sydney SMEs &#8212; retail shops, professional service firms, health and wellness businesses, local consultants and everything in between. We build affordable, tailored strategies that make the most of every marketing dollar.</p>

        <h3 class="h3">SME Businesses We Work With</h3>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Retail shops and boutiques</li>
          <li>Accountants, lawyers and financial advisers</li>
          <li>Health and wellness clinics</li>
          <li>Real estate agencies</li>
          <li>Gyms and fitness studios</li>
          <li>Childcare and education services</li>
          <li>Event planning and entertainment</li>
          <li>Fashion, beauty and personal care</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="value-col">
        <h3 style="color:#1E3A5F; font-size:1.125rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Our SME Commitment</h3>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon">??</span>
          <div>
            <strong>No big-agency minimums</strong>
            <p>We don't require $5,000/mo retainers. Our Starter plan is built for SMEs starting their digital journey.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon">??</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Every dollar tracked</strong>
            <p>Monthly reports in plain English showing exactly what your marketing budget achieved &#8212; leads, clicks, calls, revenue.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon">??</span>
          <div>
            <strong>You own everything</strong>
            <p>Your accounts, your content, your data &#8212; all in your hands. No agency lock-in or asset hostage situations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon">??</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Sydney-local knowledge</strong>
            <p>We know how Sydney customers search, shop and make decisions. No offshore generalist strategies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad" style="background: var(--bg-alt);">
    <div class="container-lg">
      <h2 class="h2 text-center">A Full Digital Strategy &#8212; Right-Sized for SMEs</h2>
      <div class="what-grid">
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Targeted Digital Ads</h3>
          <p>Google Ads and Meta campaigns with tight audience targeting &#8212; so you reach your ideal customer in Sydney, not waste budget on people who'll never buy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Local SEO</h3>
          <p>Rank higher in Google searches for your services + suburb. We optimise your Google Business Profile and build the local authority that drives organic traffic.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Social Media Management</h3>
          <p>Consistent, professional social media presence that builds trust and keeps your business top of mind &#8212; without you having to think about it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>Website That Converts</h3>
          <p>Your website should be working 24/7 generating enquiries. We build and optimise SME websites that actually convert visitors into customers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">?</span>
          <h3>Lead Generation</h3>
          <p>Full funnel from ad click to qualified enquiry in your inbox. We set up the systems that mean you wake up to new leads &#8212; not silence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card">
          <span class="what-icon">??</span>
          <h3>App Development</h3>
          <p>When you're ready to innovate &#8212; booking apps, customer portals, loyalty programs &#8212; we build custom tools that create real competitive advantage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad cta-section">
    <div class="container-lg cta-inner">
      <div>
        <h2 class="cta-heading">Let's Grow Your Sydney Business</h2>
        <p class="cta-sub">Get a free digital audit and custom growth plan. We'll look at your current online presence and tell you exactly what opportunities you're missing.</p>
        <ul class="cta-list">
          <li>&#10003; Free 30-minute strategy session</li>
          <li>&#10003; Custom plan for your budget and goals</li>
          <li>&#10003; No lock-in contracts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-form">
        <ContactForm />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .industry-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F 0%, #152b47 100%); padding: 5rem 0; text-align: center; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #FF6B35; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .hero-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .hero-title { font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.25rem); font-weight: 900; color: white; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #94afc7; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }

  .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .two-col { grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr; } }

  .h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .h3 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-heading); margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .body-text { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-body); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .text-center { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

  .service-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-body); }
  .service-list li::before { content: '\2192 '; color: #FF6B35; font-weight: 700; }

  .value-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .value-item { display: flex; gap: 0.875rem; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--surface-2); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #d1d9e6; }
  .value-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .value-item strong { display: block; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .value-item p { font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; }

  .what-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  @media (min-width: 640px)  { .what-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .what-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }

  .what-card { background: var(--surface-card); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.06); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .what-icon { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .what-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .what-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-muted); }

  .cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #e55a24 100%); }
  .cta-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  .cta-heading { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-sub { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .cta-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.625rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; }
  .cta-form { background: var(--surface-card); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.2); }
</style>

